[The Neath and Port Talbot areas are located in South Wales and Powis. Measles cases are recurring in both regions, and it is evident that although the emergency vaccination programmes have been comprehensive throughout Wales, a considerable number of school-age children remain unprotected. However, overall, the measles epidemic is in decline throughout Wales. - Mod.CP

